idataCOMMON 0 D62 1AC4 4 2
maintext 0 E07 1C0E 64 2
cstackCOMMON 1 70 70 E 1
cstackBANK0 1 20 20 4B 1
inittext 0 D84 1B08 11 2
intentry 0 4 8 7F9 2
reset_vec 0 0 0 2 2
idataBANK0 0 D77 1AEE D 2
